          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1650985458951-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the ribs and cobettes are in the oven, add the<strong> honey</strong> and <strong>smoked sea salt </strong>to the <strong>remaining vinegar mop</strong> and stir it together – this is your <strong>smoky</strong> <strong>glaze</strong></p>",
